Closes-Bug: #1256046

Block delete instance while backup

Reason:
- trove-api blocks instance-delete task
while its instance is in BUILDING state,
but instance could be deleted when its in ACTIVE
state and backup is running.
Changes:
- delete method checks if instance in BUILDING and BACKUP state;
- create_backup method sets task status to BACKUP_IN_PROGRESS;
- conductors update_backup method sets task status to NONE
before updates backup model;
- tests;

